snippet.description:

snippet.title: Bakra Nahi Majnu Halaal - Part 2 : Full On Farziwada - Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Download Skkily Ludo App From 
https://bit.ly/Amit-bhadana

REFERRAL CODE - AMIT100


Jab aag lagi hai to dhamaka to ho kar rahega. Hamare Majnu ne le lie hain bade wala panga. 2 ladkiyon ko date toh bahut log karte hain lekin hamara hero 2 sagi behnon se pyar kar baitha hani. Lalach buri bala hain Rinku na Raveena se breakup karna chahata hai aur na hi Sangeeta ko ta-ta bye-bye, aur ab vo galti se pahunch gaya hain dono ke ghar jahan bas phootne hi wala hai uska bhaanda. Kya hoga aage isi baat ka hai sabko intezaar. Kya Sangeeta aur Raveena mil kar karengi Rinku ko halal ya unke papa karenge hamare Majnu ka kaam tamaam? Kya hoga is love story ka end? Ye sab pata chalega is part mein. To sab mil kar hamare Majnu ke lie prarthna karo aur poore parivaar family ke sath dekho ye kamaal dhamaal story. Dhnyaawad :)

In this video, Abhi and Niyu discuss RBI's Special Vostro Account plan to make Rupee an International currency. Now NRIs will be able to use UPI to transfer money in 10 countries. snippet.title: सनी देओल ने अमृता सिंह को दी 'किस' की सज़ा - Betaab - Sunny Deol, Amrita Singh, Shammi Kapoor
snippet.description:
Subscribe To Shemaroo Movie in Parts: https://www.youtube.com/user/shemaroopremiumfilms?sub_confirmation=1

This film is a love story of two youngsters who fall in love despite the status gaps between their families. Sunny, is a young, poor and happy guy who lives with his mother Sumitra in his home-made town farm. Formerly, his father Avenash had been a big businessman, but he went bankrupt. For this reason, he killed himself. Avenash was close friends with Sardar Dinesh Singh Girji who is one of the richest and most powerful men in the city. When Sardar reveals that Avenash has gone bankrupt, he turns his back to him. Sardar has one daughter called Roma. She is spoiled, snobbish and accustomed to having all the people who surround her beneath her. She was Sunny's childhood friend.

Now, Sardar purchases a new horse farm out of the city in the town, which is nearby Sunny's farm. When Sunny accompanies his mother to the train station, he encounters Roma after not seeing her for years. Sunny instantly recognizes her, but Roma doesn't. Consequently, they coincidentally meet each other various times on the farm. They quarrel continually, but soon she realises that he is her childhood friend and they reconstruct their childhood love.

Directed by Rahul Rawail
Written by Javed Akhtar
Produced by Bikram Singh Dahal
Starring - Shammi Kapoor, Sunny Deol, Amrita Singh, Nirupa Roy, Prem Chopra, Rehana
Cinematography Manmohan Singh
Music by Rahul Dev Burman

यह फिल्म दो युवाओं की प्रेम कहानी है जो अपने परिवारों के बीच स्थिति के अंतर के बावजूद प्यार में पड़ जाते हैं। सनी, एक युवा, गरीब और खुशमिजाज लड़का है जो अपनी मां सुमित्रा के साथ अपने घर के कस्बे के खेत में रहता है। उनके पिता अविनाश पहले बड़े बिजनेसमैन थे, लेकिन उनका दिवालिया हो गया। इसी वजह से उसने अपनी जान दे दी। अवनाश सरदार दिनेश सिंह गिरजी के करीबी दोस्त थे जो शहर के सबसे अमीर और सबसे शक्तिशाली व्यक्तियों में से एक हैं। जब सरदार को पता चलता है कि अविनाश दिवालिया हो गया है, तो वह उसकी ओर पीठ कर लेता है। सरदार की एक बेटी है जिसका नाम रोमा है। वह बिगड़ैल है, दंभी है और अपने आसपास के सभी लोगों को अपने नीचे रखने की आदी है। वह सनी की बचपन की दोस्त थी।

अब, सरदार शहर के बाहर कस्बे में एक नया घोड़ा फार्म खरीदता है, जो सनी के खेत के पास है। जब सनी अपनी मां के साथ ट्रेन स्टेशन जाता है, तो सालों तक रोमा को न देखने के बाद उसका सामना रोमा से होता है। सनी तुरंत उसे पहचान लेती है, लेकिन रोमा नहीं। नतीजतन, वे संयोग से खेत पर कई बार एक-दूसरे से मिलते हैं। वे लगातार झगड़ते हैं, लेकिन जल्द ही उसे पता चलता है कि वह उसका बचपन का दोस्त है और वे अपने बचपन के प्यार का पुनर्निर्माण करते हैं।

संचालन राहुल रवैल ने किया
जावेद अख्तर द्वारा लिखित
बिक्रम सिंह दहल द्वारा निर्मित
कलाकार - शम्मी कपूर, सनी देओल, अमृता सिंह, निरूपा रॉय, प्रेम चोपड़ा, रेहाना
छायांकन मनमोहन सिंह
संगीत राहुल देव बर्मन ने दिया है

localized.title: सनी देओल ने अमृता सिंह को दी 'किस' की सज़ा - Betaab - Sunny Deol, Amrita Singh, Shammi Kapoor
localized.description:
Subscribe To Shemaroo Movie in Parts: https://www.youtube.com/user/shemaroopremiumfilms?sub_confirmation=1

This film is a love story of two youngsters who fall in love despite the status gaps between their families. Sunny, is a young, poor and happy guy who lives with his mother Sumitra in his home-made town farm. Formerly, his father Avenash had been a big businessman, but he went bankrupt. For this reason, he killed himself. Avenash was close friends with Sardar Dinesh Singh Girji who is one of the richest and most powerful men in the city. When Sardar reveals that Avenash has gone bankrupt, he turns his back to him. Sardar has one daughter called Roma. She is spoiled, snobbish and accustomed to having all the people who surround her beneath her. She was Sunny's childhood friend.

Now, Sardar purchases a new horse farm out of the city in the town, which is nearby Sunny's farm. When Sunny accompanies his mother to the train station, he encounters Roma after not seeing her for years. Sunny instantly recognizes her, but Roma doesn't. Consequently, they coincidentally meet each other various times on the farm. They quarrel continually, but soon she realises that he is her childhood friend and they reconstruct their childhood love.

Directed by Rahul Rawail
Written by Javed Akhtar
Produced by Bikram Singh Dahal
Starring - Shammi Kapoor, Sunny Deol, Amrita Singh, Nirupa Roy, Prem Chopra, Rehana
Cinematography Manmohan Singh
Music by Rahul Dev Burman

snippet.title: DAMaN (In Hindi) Official Trailer | Babushaan Mohanty, Dipanwit D | In Cinemas 3rd February 2023
snippet.description:
In 2015, a young doctor, Dr. Siddharth Mohanty, who has just completed his MBBS from a government medical college, is posted  to a back of beyond tribal area in the Malkangiri district. Janbai PHC has 151 villages under it, is  infamous for its Naxal dominance and doesn't even boast of the most basic facilities. 
Dr. Siddharth Mohanty arrives reluctantly, wanting to quit at the earliest. But fate wills otherwise.  Daman is the story of 151 villages and one doctor to control the spread of malaria, the tussle between superstition and medical science. 

Presenting you the official trailer of DAMaN in Hindi.

en-IN.title: DAMaN (In Hindi) Official Trailer | Babushaan Mohanty, Dipanwit D | In Cinemas 3rd February 2023
en-IN.description:
In 2015, a young doctor, Dr. Siddharth Mohanty, who has just completed his MBBS from a government medical college, is posted  to a back of beyond tribal area in the Malkangiri district. Janbai PHC has 151 villages under it, is  infamous for its Naxal dominance and doesn't even boast of the most basic facilities. 
Dr. Siddharth Mohanty arrives reluctantly, wanting to quit at the earliest. But fate wills otherwise.  Daman is the story of 151 villages and one doctor to control the spread of malaria, the tussle between superstition and medical science. 

Presenting you the official trailer of DAMaN in Hindi.

snippet.title: Kanuma Special Ratham muggulu designs🌺Beautiful Chariot rangoli & kolam
snippet.description:
Kanuma Special Ratham muggulu designs🌺Beautiful Chariot rangoli & kolam.
Kolam or muggu is a ancient art form of India which is very popular.
Kolam is also called as Rangoli in parts of India.
women create different kolam or rangoli designs infront of the doorstep in the early morning
taking ideas from the nature like flowers,deepams,diyas,animals like elephants,cows, fruits, birds likev peacock and swan etc.
In Andhra pradesh and Telangana, kolam designs are called muggulu.
Rangoli or kolam designs are drawn with dots like 5 dots, 6 dots and so on and without dots also (freehand rangoli).
People celebrate festivals like Diwali,Sankranthi (Pongal), Ganesh Chathurthi,Dasara( Vijaya dasami) by drawing different 
creative Kolam or rangoli designs with different colors and flowers in fornt of their houses.
People draw Beautiful special kolams on Friday to get the blessings of Godess Lakshmi.
Designs vary from easy rangoli for beginners to difficult levels for professionals.
#rangoli #kolam #muggulu

snippet.description:
अभी 2 दिन और कड़ाके की सर्दी पड़ेगी तथा बर्फीली सर्द हवाएं परेशान करेंगी। जम्मू-कश्मीर हिमाचल प्रदेश उत्तराखंड से लेकर पंजाब हरियाणा दिल्ली उत्तर प्रदेश मध्य प्रदेश छत्तीसगढ़ राजस्थान गुजरात और महाराष्ट्र तक कड़ाके की सर्दी बनी रहेगी। 10 जनवरी से नया पश्चिमी विक्षोभ पहाड़ों पर बर्फबारी देना शुरू करेगा उसके प्रभाव से 23 और 24 तारीख से 25 तारीख तक मैदानी भागों में बारिश संभव है कहीं कहीं ओलावृष्टि भी हो सकती है।

snippet.title: Oh Ni Reh Gaya Yaara (Full Video) Harbhajan Mann | Babu Singh Maan | Laddi Gill | New Punjabi Songs
snippet.description:
Subscribe to HM Records : http://bit.ly/HMRecords

“ਉਹ ਨੀ ਰਹਿ ਗਿਆ ਯਾਰਾ” , ਤੁਹਾਡੀ, ਮੇਰੀ ਸਭ ਦੀ ਕਹਾਣੀ ਹੈ। ਆਪਣਿਆਂ ਤੋਂ ਮਿਲੇ ਜ਼ਖਮ ਤੇ ਧੋਖੇ ਇਨਸਾਨ ਨੂੰ ਸਭ ਤੋਂ ਵੱਧ ਤਕਲੀਫ਼ ਦਿੰਦੇ ਆ। “ਬਾਬੂ ਸਿੰਘ ਮਾਨ” ਸਾਹਬ ਦੀ ਕਲਮ, ਜ਼ਿੰਦਗੀ ਦੇ ਇਸ ਸੱਚ ਨੂੰ ਬਿਆਨ ਕਰ ਰਹੀ ਹੈ। “ਲਾਡੀ ਗਿੱਲ” ਦਾ ਬਹੁਤ ਹੀ ਪਿਆਰਾ ਸੰਗੀਤ ਤੇ ਸਟਾਲਿਨਵੀਰ ਦਾ ਮਿਹਨਤ ਨਾਲ ਤਿਆਰ ਕੀਤਾ ਇਹ ਵੀਡਿਓ, ਆਸ ਹੈ ਤੁਹਾਨੂੰ ਬਹੁਤ ਪਸੰਦ ਆਏਗਾ।

HM Records present "Oh Ni Reh Gaya Yaara", the latest track from the album "My Way: Main Te Mere Geet". Beautifully written by Babu Singh Maan, with fine musical treatment by Laddi Gill and wonderfully visualized by Stalinveer, the song illustrates the trials and tribulations that occur in friendships, and it is sure to strike a chord with any person who has gone through similar experiences.

Song Credits:

Singer: Harbhajan Mann
Lyrics: Babu Singh Maan
Music: Laddi Gill
Composer: Harbhajan Mann
Mix & Master: MJ

Video Credits:

Director: Stalinveer
DOP: Jaspreet Jassi
Editor: Harmeet S Kalra
Cast: Manjot Benipal, Sukhpal Bajwa, Meet Dhiman, Paramjit Kaur, Jot Jassar, Avideep & Karnav
Production: Balli Dhaliwal
Location: Singla Farm House
Producer: Gurvinder Singh
Label: HM Records

Farq Episode 23 - [Eng Sub] - Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 16th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

snippet.title: 15 जनवरी का मौसम: आधे से ज्यादा हिंदुस्तान में शीतलहर। 23 जनवरी से उत्तर भारत में बारिश के आसार
snippet.description:
बर्फ से लदे पहाड़ों से बहने वाली सर्द हवाएं आधे से ज्यादा हिंदुस्तान का तापमान गिराएंगी। राजस्थान में पारा शून्य से नीचे हरियाणा में भी शून्य के आसपास तापमान हो सकता है। 19 तारीख से नया पश्चिमी विक्षोभ पहाड़ों पर बर्फबारी देगा तथा मैदानी भागों के तापमान बढ़ने लगेंगे। 23 और 24 जनवरी से पंजाब हरियाणा उत्तर प्रदेश दिल्ली उत्तरी मध्य प्रदेश तथा उत्तरी राजस्थान में बारिश के आसार हैं।

snippet.title: #video दरवाजा खुला छोड़ आई - #SamarSingh & #ShilpiRaj New Song | Akansha Dubey | Bhojpuri Song 2023
snippet.description:
टिप्स भोजपुरी प्रस्तुत करता है 90s का सबसे मस्ती भरा धमाकेदार गाना "दरवाजा खुला छोड़ आई" एक नए अंदाज में Samar Singh और Shilpi Raj की आवाज में.

अगर अच्छा लगे तो ज्यादा से ज्यादा शेयर और हमारे चैनल को सब्सक्राइब करे 
https://www.youtube.com/tipsBhojpuri

Song Credits:
Song Name: Darwaja Khula Chhod Aayi
Singer: Samar Singh, Shilpi Raj
Lyricist: Prakash Barud
Music: Sarvind Malhar

Video Credits:
Featuring: Akansha Dubey & Samar Singh
Video Director: Goldie Jaiswal
Choreographer: Bobby Jackson
DOP: Sunil Baba, Brijesh Yadav
Makeup: Pankaj Dada
Hair Stylist: Priyanka Singh
Editor: Pappu Verma 
DI: Rohit Singh
Production: Abhay Pandey

For Movie & Album Please Get in Touch with:
Mr. Vijay Kashyap - +91 98100 34523 - vijayk@tips.in

Lyrics:
M:बोल काहे खाती कईले बाडु कॉल हो
घर के ठिक ठाक बाटे न माहौल हो
F:हम नाही जननी देवर घर में बाड़े
दरवाजा दरवाजा खुला छोड़ आई निंद के मारे

M:रह संभर के घर में ए रानी
अपना जवानी के कर निगरानी
F:भर दिन होखतावे खटानी राजा जी
बडी बानी लाचार कहतानी राजा जी
टेंशन से भारी भईल कपारे
दरवाजा दरवाजा खुला छोड़ आई निंद के मारे

M:तोहरो में बाटे ए रानी दोष हो
सुतेलू एक दम होके बेहोश हो
F:बडी बिगड़ल देवर समर बडूए
खाली ताकत हमार कमर बडुए 
प्रकाश बारूद नहीं सुते दुआरे
दरवाजा खुला छोड़ आई निंद के मा

snippet.title: Mitthye Premer Gaan (মিথ্যে প্রেমের গান) | Official Trailer | Anirban,Ishaa,Arjun | Paroma
snippet.description:
প্রেম চির অন্ধ। কখনও সম্পূর্ণ দুই বিপরীত চরিত্রের মানুষও প্রেমে পড়ে। তেমনই প্রেমকাহিনী অভীক আর অন্বেষার গল্প। পরমা নেওটিয়া পরিচালিত, অনির্বাণ ভট্টাচার্য, ইশা সাহা, অর্জুন চক্রবর্তী অভিনীত 'মিথ্যে প্রেমের গান' আসছে আগামী ১০ ফেব্রুয়ারি আপনার নিকটবর্তী প্রেক্ষাগৃহে। রইল এই ছবির ট্রেলার কেবলমাত্র SVF এ।
A reclusive, introverted singer-songwriter falls in love with an ambitious, pragmatic girl who changes how he sees the world and himself.
Mitthye Premer Gaan is coming to a theatre near you this 10th February. Come, witness, the flawed fairytale of Avik, Anwesha and Aditya.

Cast: Anirban Bhattacharya, Ishaa Saha, Arjun Chakrabarty, Soumya Mukherjee, Anusha Viswanathan, Sudipa Bose, Debesh Chattopadhyay, Biswarup Biswas

Special Thanks: Shrikant Mohta

 Nayantara: After 10 years of marriage, Adidev (Gourab Mondal) and Averi (Payal De) are about to experience parenthood with the birth of their first child. The doctor warns Avery that she might face life threatening complications if she decides to go ahead with the child birth. snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3669 - 16 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3669: Bawri Vapas Aagayi
--------------------------------------------------------
Bawri arrives in Gokuldham and surprises everyone. Bagha breaks down when he sees his love, Bawri. Bawri is bombarded with inquiries about her sudden disappearance. She explains to everyone that everything happened because of a minor misunderstanding. Her hair color was messed up by a salon called "Baby," and instead of texting them, she texted Bagha. In any case, everyone is relieved that Bagha and Bawri are reunited. Bhide suggests to Madhavi that Bawri's return may be a problem disguised as an opportunity. Nattu Kaka and Bagha later go missing. Keep an eye out!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3669, 16 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000204923

Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 06 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 06 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 12th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

snippet.title: Sweet Pongal Recipe in Tamil | Sakkarai Pongal Recipe in Tamil | Chakkarai Pongal
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make sweet pongal recipe in tamil. Sakkarai pongal is a great recipe which brings back so many warm memories, the soft fluffy cooked rice and dal with jaggery and roasted nuts is a great way to start the morning. This is pongal recipe is very easy to make and we can make pongal either in a pot or in a pressure cooker.


Sweet Pongal in pot :- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ESuqXoJj4M0
Sweet Pongal in cooker :- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AgWLO_cV7zw

Wish you all a very happy Pongal 2023 and have fun. Also, please do make this sweet pongal and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!

Ingredients:
1 cup Raw Rice
1/2 cup Moong Dal
1 cup Milk
1 cup rinsed Water
4.5-5 cup Water
2 cup Jaggery
4+4 tbsp Ghee
1/2 coconut pieces
1/4 cup Cashews
2 tbsp Raisins
1/2 tsp Cardamom
pinch of Salt

Radhakrishn Raasleela - Part 276 | Krishn Ki Yojana | Radhakrishn | राधाकृष्ण
Radhakrishn Raasleela - Part 276 | Krishn Ki Yojana | Radhakrishn | राधाकृष्ण

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!


Jaanne ke liye dekhiye #RadhaKrishn, Somvaar se Shanivaar, shaam 7.30 baje, sirf #StarBharat par. Krishn aur Radha ki leelaon se judde rehne ke liye hamein follow kariye Instagram, Facebook aur YouTube par!

Radhakrishn Raasleela - Part 276 | Krishn Ki Yojana | Radhakrishn | राधाकृष्ण

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!


Jaanne ke liye dekhiye #RadhaKrishn, Somvaar se Shanivaar, shaam 7.30 baje, sirf #StarBharat par. Krishn aur Radha ki leelaon se judde rehne ke liye hamein follow kariye Instagram, Facebook aur YouTube par!

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3688 - 14 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3668: Nashe Mein Bagha
--------------------------------------------------------
Bagha is asked to leave the balcony's end and come to the compound by Anjali, who is costumed as Bawari. As soon as Bagha notices her, he instantly descends from the balcony and proposes to her. He decides to return to the balcony after realizing the woman is not Bawri. Bagha is apprehended by the Gokuldham society members and taken to Dr. Hathi's office, where he receives treatment to end his intoxication. Stay tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3668, 14 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000204586

snippet.title: Rasathi (Video Song) | Shankar Mahadevan • Anthony Daasan • KJ Iyenar | @mmoriginalstamil ​
snippet.description:
​@mmoriginalstamil #MMOriginals proudly presents #Rasathi, a peppy folk number composed & sung by Shankar Mahadevan. Featuring ‘’Folk Marley’’ Antony Dasan along with Super Singer Fame rapper K J Iyenar.

The lyrics are by Pa.Vijay and the rap is written by Iyenar. This lively song is further picturised as a quirky video that features Roshini Haripriyan of Barathi Kannamma & Cook with Comali fame along with Shankar Mahadevan, Antony Dasan & Iyenar. Groove to ‘Rasathi’ with #shorts  & #reels.

*About* 
------------

Judwa behene Divya aur Drishti ko apne janam se mila hai shakti ka vardaan. Drishti bhavishya kaal ko dekh sakti hai aur Divya ussey badal sakti hai. Inke mata pita ne apni jaan ka balidaan dekar bachaya dono beheno ko par bichad gaye bachpan mai Divya aur Drishti. Alag alag parivaaron mai pale bade par ek doosre ko dhundhte rahe. 
Ek kaali shakti - Pishaachini haasil karna chahti hai sarva shaktishali Kaal Vijay Ratna ko aur saalon se padi hai dono beheno ke peeche. Dobara mil hi jaati hai Divya aur Drishti. Ek saath milkar karti hai muqaabla Pishaachini ka aur karte hai waada ussey khatam karne ka.

snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

With an intention to stop Thapki from meeting Bihaan and his family, Shraddha shows her the papers that could put Bihaan behind bars. Will Thapki bow down to her threats?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: പ്രവീണ്‍ റാണയ്ക്ക് വിനയായത് നിക്ഷേപകരുടെ യോഗവും ആ വോയ്‌സ് ക്ലിപ്പും | Safe & Strong Fraud Case
snippet.description:
തൃശ്ശൂരിലെ സെയ്ഫ് ആന്‍ഡ് സ്‌ട്രോങ് നിക്ഷേപത്തട്ടിപ്പ് കേസില്‍ കമ്പനി എംഡി പ്രവീണ്‍ റാണയ്ക്ക് വിനയായത് നിക്ഷേപകരുടെ യോഗവും തുടര്‍ന്ന് അയച്ച വോയ്‌സ് ക്ലിപ്പും. വര്‍ഷങ്ങളോളം നൂറുകണക്കിന് നിക്ഷേപകരെ സമര്‍ത്ഥമായി പറ്റിച്ച റാണ, ഡിസംബര്‍ 27-ന് വിളിച്ച യോഗത്തിലൂടെ സ്വയം കുഴി തോണ്ടുകയായിരുന്നു. ഈ യോഗമാണ് വഞ്ചിക്കപ്പെട്ടവരുടെ കൂട്ടായ്മ രൂപീകരിക്കാനും തുടര്‍ന്ന് കേസുകള്‍ നല്‍കാനും കാരണമായതെന്ന് സെയ്ഫ് & സ്‌ട്രോങ് കസ്റ്റമര്‍ വെല്‍ഫെയര്‍ അസോസിയേഷന്‍ പ്രസിഡന്റ് രാജന്‍ ജോസഫ് പറയുന്നു.

snippet.title: Paresh Rawal Comedy - चिट्टी के चचेरे भाई औकात भूल गया, ऊंट की गर्दन खुजायेगा तू | Scene Compilation
snippet.description:
Janardhan Wishvanbhar Rane, a widower, has spent his life bringing up his two kids Chirag and Gaurav. Now when the two have grown up, Gaurav takes up his father's responsibility. They manage the household chores and their business as well. One day Gaurav meets his college friend Sheekha Kapoor, who lives with her guardian Anuradha who was Janardan's first love. Gaurav and Sheekha come to know about their past relationship. Now Gaurav wants his father to marry Anuradha.

Movie - Mere Baap Pehle Aap
Starcast - Akshaye Khanna, Paresh Rawal, Genelia D'Souza, Rajpal Yadav, Archana Puran Singh
Director - Priyadarshan

#merebaappehleaap #comedyscenes #pareshrawalcomedy

जनार्दन विश्वनभर राणे, एक विधुर, ने अपना जीवन अपने दो बच्चों चिराग और गौरव को पालने में बिताया है। अब जब दोनों बड़े हो गए हैं तो गौरव ने अपने पिता की जिम्मेदारी उठा ली है। वे घर का काम और अपना व्यवसाय भी संभालती हैं। एक दिन गौरव अपनी कॉलेज की दोस्त शिखा कपूर से मिलता है, जो अपनी अभिभावक अनुराधा के साथ रहती है, जो जनार्दन का पहला प्यार थी। गौरव और शिखा को अपने पिछले रिश्ते के बारे में पता चल जाता है। अब गौरव चाहता है कि उसके पिता अनुराधा से शादी कर लें।

फिल्म - मेरे बाप पहले आप
स्टारकास्ट - अक्षय खन्ना, परेश रावल, जेनेलिया डिसूजा, राजपाल यादव, अर्चना पूरन सिंह
निर्देशक - प्रियदर्शन

जनार्दन विश्वनभर राणे, एक विधुर, ने अपना जीवन अपने दो बच्चों चिराग और गौरव को पालने में बिताया है। अब जब दोनों बड़े हो गए हैं तो गौरव ने अपने पिता की जिम्मेदारी उठा ली है। वे घर का काम और अपना व्यवसाय भी संभालती हैं। एक दिन गौरव अपनी कॉलेज की दोस्त शिखा कपूर से मिलता है, जो अपनी अभिभावक अनुराधा के साथ रहती है, जो जनार्दन का पहला प्यार थी। गौरव और शिखा को अपने पिछले रिश्ते के बारे में पता चल जाता है। अब गौरव चाहता है कि उसके पिता अनुराधा से शादी कर लें।

இன்று இந்தியன் ரெசிபி தமிழில், கேரட்டின் மிகவும் புதிய, சுவையான  ரெசிபியை நான் கொண்டு வந்துள்ளேன், இது போன்ற சில விஷயங்களைக் கொண்ட அருமையான ரெசிபியை நீங்கள் பார்த்திருக்க மாட்டீர்கள், மேலும் இது மிகவும் எளிதானது. எனவே கேரட் இனிப்பு செய்முறையை கண்டிப்பாக பாருங்கள். கேரட் டெசர்ட் ரெசிபிகள் | இந்த கேரட் டிலைட் ரெசிபியை பகிர மறக்காதீர்கள் by indian Recipes tamil | Indian recipes tamil | அபியின் செய்முறை

Ingredients:
Carrot - 500 gms
Water - 500 ml
Corn Flour - 3 tbsp
Sugar Powder - 1/2 cup

* தேவையான பொருட்கள்:
கேரட் - 500 கிராம்
தண்ணீர் - 500 மிலி
சோள மாவு - 3 டீஸ்பூன்
சர்க்கரை தூள் - 1/2 கப்
